#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1283
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To make the Wake-On-LAN feature work, you must provide the MAC address of "
#| "the server you selected. Currently, &smb4k; has no way to determine the "
#| "MAC address, so you need to find it on your own. Afterwards, you can "
#| "define if &smb4k; should send a magic Wake-On-LAN package to the selected "
